01.12.2001

1. U-Hexen project is started on sourceforge.net 

03.12.2001 

1. Fixed the finale lump search. 
If U-Hexen doen't find this lump it simply displays "congradulations!" message.
My hexen.wad does not contain these lumps, I don't know why.
2. U-Hexen can now play demo wad. And it can be distributed with this IWAD.
3. Version 0.6 is out.

04.12.2001

1. Fixed palette handling (problems with DirectX).
2. Added 24 bpp surface support.
3. Fixed save path on Windows.
4. Version 0.61 is out.
